<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 18:08:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>超过 50 名国际广播记者呼吁埃及和以色列允许“自由和不受限制”进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/over-50-intl-broadcast-journalists-call-on-egypt-and-israel-to-allow-free-access-to-gaza/0000018d-f0a9-d7f4-a3dd-f6ad7cdf0000</link><description>这封信由美国有线电视新闻网（CNN）和英国广播公司（BBC）等媒体的资深记者签署，呼吁以色列允许外国记者进入加沙，而不必“嵌入”以色列国防军，并呼吁埃及允许进入拉法口岸。它还要求以色列尊重当地巴勒斯坦记者的安全</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 17:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/over-50-intl-broadcast-journalists-call-on-egypt-and-israel-to-allow-free-access-to-gaza/0000018d-f0a9-d7f4-a3dd-f6ad7cdf0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 145 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-145/0000018d-f089-d7f4-a3dd-f68d05d70000</link><description>哈马斯政治局主席哈尼亚表示，该组织在释放人质/停火谈判方面持灵活态度，但已做好继续战斗的准备，并呼吁穆斯林在斋月第一天加固阿克萨清真寺。 ■ 以色列国防军：160 包人道主义援助物资空投到叙利亚加沙南部 ■ 哈马斯和法塔赫代表团将于周四在莫斯科会面，讨论组建统一的巴勒斯坦政府 ■ 战争结束 145 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 17:35:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-145/0000018d-f089-d7f4-a3dd-f68d05d70000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦外长表示与哈马斯关于统一政府的谈判预计不会出现“奇迹”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/palestinian-seminister-no-miracles-expected-at-talks-on-unified-government/0000018d-f04e-dd8a-a5af-f87ecf160000</link><description>巴勒斯坦总理穆罕默德·什塔耶辞职几天后，哈马斯和法塔赫代表定于周四在莫斯科举行会谈</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 16:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/palestinian-seminister-no-miracles-expected-at-talks-on-unified-government/0000018d-f04e-dd8a-a5af-f87ecf160000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC 解释道：美国强大且分裂的亲以色列游说团体的内幕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/aipac-explained-the-inside-story-of-americas-powerful-and-divisive-pro-israel-lobby/0000018d-e4ac-d972-a5bf-efaf96c60000</link><description>美国以色列公共事务委员会与美国总统和政客发生冲突、纵容、针对和支持，使以色列成为一个日益党派化的问题。以下是您需要了解的有关 AIPAC 的信息，这是一个令人尊敬、令人恐惧和谩骂的游说和政治筹款组织，准备在 2024 年的选举中发挥巨大作用</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 16:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/aipac-explained-the-inside-story-of-americas-powerful-and-divisive-pro-israel-lobby/0000018d-e4ac-d972-a5bf-efaf96c60000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦-以色列和平活动家二人组被《时代》杂志评为年度女性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-israeli-peace-activist-duo-named-among-time-magazines-women-of-the-year/0000018d-f04a-dd0a-afcf-ffde7c740000</link><description>“妇女争取和平”和“太阳妇女”这两个组织形成了所谓的“伙伴关系协定”，誓言“坚定、坚持和相互尊重地共同努力”，以结束以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:42:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-israeli-peace-activist-duo-named-among-time-magazines-women-of-the-year/0000018d-f04a-dd0a-afcf-ffde7c740000</guid></item><item><title>《欣快感》明星在接受拜登采访时抗议以色列和加沙战争时被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/euphoria-star-arrested-while-protesting-against-israel-war-in-gaza-at-biden-interview/0000018d-efd4-dd0a-afcf-efd698060000</link><description>在 JVP Instagram 上分享的一篇帖子中，亨特·谢弗 (Hunter Schafer) 与其他示威者坐在一起，身穿印有“立即停火”字样的 T 恤。该组织还发布了抗议视频，视频中女演员和其他人高呼“不再有武器，不再有战争，停火是我们奋斗的目标”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:18:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/euphoria-star-arrested-while-protesting-against-israel-war-in-gaza-at-biden-interview/0000018d-efd4-dd0a-afcf-efd698060000</guid></item><item><title>向以色列高等法院提交请愿书，反对教育部长不授予以色列奖的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/high-court-petition-filed-against-education-ministers-decision-not-to-award-israel-prize/0000018d-f01e-dd8a-a5af-f87e2cb70000</link><description>请愿书认为，根据以色列奖项规定，教育部长无权取消奖项类别。 “对这些决定的唯一不幸的解释是教育部长接管该奖项的尝试是完全不可接受的”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/high-court-petition-filed-against-education-ministers-decision-not-to-award-israel-prize/0000018d-f01e-dd8a-a5af-f87e2cb70000</guid></item><item><title>该国的宗教右翼意识形态正在以色列造成劳动力紧缩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/the-states-religious-right-ideology-is-creating-a-labor-crunch-in-israel/0000018d-f032-d7f4-a3dd-f63ee6870000</link><description>多年来，以色列经济的快速增长是由稳定增长的劳动力市场推动的。现在政府似乎正在竭尽全力缩小规模</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/the-states-religious-right-ideology-is-creating-a-labor-crunch-in-israel/0000018d-f032-d7f4-a3dd-f63ee6870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列顶级厨师开设特拉维夫最好的冰淇淋店</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/food/2024-02-28/ty-article-review/.premium/have-you-already-tasted-tel-avivs-best-ice-cream-place/0000018d-efc3-d1e0-a1dd-fff7da3f0000</link><description>洋甘菊黑胡椒、薰衣草蜂蜜和烤米饭：厨师 Eyal Shani 的新冰淇淋吧提供城里最好的冰淇淋（而且排得很长）</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:09:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/food/2024-02-28/ty-article-review/.premium/have-you-already-tasted-tel-avivs-best-ice-cream-place/0000018d-efc3-d1e0-a1dd-fff7da3f0000</guid></item><item><title>“当我的演讲被称为反犹太主义时，我感到震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-my-speech-was-called-antisemitic-i-was-shocked/0000018d-efc4-dd8a-a5af-effe1d7c0000</link><description>获得柏林电影节最佳纪录片奖本应是以色列电影制片人尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕职业生涯的顶峰。对《No Other Land》获奖感言的回应让他感到震惊，但他并没有陷入沉默</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:27:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-my-speech-was-called-antisemitic-i-was-shocked/0000018d-efc4-dd8a-a5af-effe1d7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙北部战斗中丧生的以色列军官的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-two-israeli-officers-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-ef6e-d401-a3dd-ef7e03ae0000</link><description>Iftah Shahar 少校，25 岁​​，Cap。吉瓦蒂旅 24 岁的伊泰·赛义夫 (Itai Seif) 在简易爆炸装置被触发时身亡。以色列国防军称，另外七名士兵也在爆炸中受重伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:17:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-two-israeli-officers-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-ef6e-d401-a3dd-ef7e03ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列地方选举：极端正统派、极右派在全国各地取得进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-local-elections-ultra-orthodox-far-right-make-gains-across-country/0000018d-eec3-d7f4-a3dd-eecfa37b0000</link><description>极端正统派和极右宗教犹太复国主义政党将在耶路撒冷取得压倒性胜利，而南部城市米兹佩·拉蒙将迎来一位以极右观点闻名的利库德集团市长。特拉维夫和海法仍然是自由派的据点</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:32:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-local-elections-ultra-orthodox-far-right-make-gains-across-country/0000018d-eec3-d7f4-a3dd-eecfa37b0000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼以色列定居者因西岸暴力风险将继续被拘留，未经审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-settler-to-remain-in-detention-without-trial-over-risk-of-violence/0000018d-ee97-d05b-addd-ee97659c0000</link><description>以色列国防部长决定，由于阿里尔·达尼诺 (Ariel Danino) 可能在约旦河西岸煽动暴力，继 10 月份初次拘留后，将再对其实施行政拘留三个月</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:51:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-settler-to-remain-in-detention-without-trial-over-risk-of-violence/0000018d-ee97-d05b-addd-ee97659c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯之间的人质释放、停火谈判立场如何？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/where-do-the-hostage-release-talks-between-israel-and-hamas-stand-what-are-the-gaps/0000018d-ec6b-dd0a-afcf-efff7b040000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯都有兴趣在下个月斋月开始前达成释放人质的协议，但尽管最近几天的乐观情绪仍然存在，但仍然存在许多障碍</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/where-do-the-hostage-release-talks-between-israel-and-hamas-stand-what-are-the-gaps/0000018d-ec6b-dd0a-afcf-efff7b040000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列国防军坦克至少五次错误地向以色列领土开火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-tanks-mistakenly-fired-inside-israeli-territory-at-least-five-times-since-start-of-war/0000018d-eb5e-d401-a3dd-eb5e50570000</link><description>有一次，以色列和黎巴嫩边境沿线的哈尼塔集体农场发射了两枚炮弹，炸毁了两栋房屋；另一次，在加沙发射的一枚炮弹击中了斯德洛特市政厅。以色列国防军回应：“吸取了必要的教训”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:02:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-tanks-mistakenly-fired-inside-israeli-territory-at-least-five-times-since-start-of-war/0000018d-eb5e-d401-a3dd-eb5e50570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩真主党目标；人质家属游行前往耶路撒冷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-live/sirens-sound-in-southern-israel-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon/0000018d-ed87-d7f4-a3dd-ef8fa5460000</link><description>什莫纳市建筑遭黎巴嫩发射袭击 ■ 拜登表示，他希望下周能达成停火协议 ■ 消息人士称，哈马斯正在研究巴黎停火提案，涉及 40 天停火和交换人质 ■ 哈马斯卫生部称加沙最后一天有96人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:25:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-live/sirens-sound-in-southern-israel-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon/0000018d-ed87-d7f4-a3dd-ef8fa5460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列第一家 Shake Shack 在特拉维夫开业，但理由并不稳固</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-first-shake-shack-opens-in-tel-aviv-on-shaky-grounds/0000018d-eb52-d1e0-a1dd-fbf7b4190000</link><description>在支持巴勒斯坦的呼吁抵制以及细心的犹太人的失望叹息中，以色列获得了第一个 Shake Shack 汉堡店，这让我们的记者回忆起更简单、更奶酪的时代</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:45:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-first-shake-shack-opens-in-tel-aviv-on-shaky-grounds/0000018d-eb52-d1e0-a1dd-fbf7b4190000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间以色列地方选举投票率低，公众冷漠</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/low-turnout-in-israels-local-elections-amid-war-in-gaza-public-apathy/0000018d-ec43-d05b-addd-eec305be0000</link><description>全天投票率仍然很低，只有不到一半的合格选民投票</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:42:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/low-turnout-in-israels-local-elections-amid-war-in-gaza-public-apathy/0000018d-ec43-d05b-addd-eec305be0000</guid></item><item><title>这个斋月，以色列极右翼部长会放火还是会被遏制？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-27/ty-article/.highlight/this-ramadan-will-israels-far-right-ministers-set-fires-or-be-reined-in/0000018d-ebc0-d401-a3dd-ebda30fd0000</link><description>用你自己的混合比喻来说，看起来这种噪音不会在基地门口停止，格兰特先生。是时候遏制你们党的领导人拉拢的不负责任的行为者了</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 19:51:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-27/ty-article/.highlight/this-ramadan-will-israels-far-right-ministers-set-fires-or-be-reined-in/0000018d-ebc0-d401-a3dd-ebda30fd0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 144 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-144/0000018d-eb6f-d401-a3dd-eb7f2a0f0000</link><description>拜登：如果达成释放人质/停火协议，以色列愿意在斋月期间停止加沙战斗，希望下周一能达成协议 ■ 一位以色列高级消息人士告诉美国广播公司新闻，内塔尼亚胡总理对拜登的言论感到惊讶 ■ 哈马斯官员称该组织正在研究巴黎制定的最新提案，但双方之间仍存在巨大差距 ■ 这是战争开始 144 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 16:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-144/0000018d-eb6f-d401-a3dd-eb7f2a0f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>